			"level": 3,
			"entries": [
"You gain proficiency with simple and martial weapons and and gain training with medium and heavy armor and shields. Additionally, you ignore the Strength requirements of Heavy weapons and armor. When you make a melee weapon attack, you can use your Charisma modifier for the attack and damage rolls instead of using Strength and can increase your reach by 10 feet until the end of your next turn."
				]
