			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Law Mage",
			"subclassSource": "LawMageWizard",
			"level": 6,
			"entries": [
"You can wield your weapon with the might of magic rather than your hands. Whenever you equip a weapon, you can have it magically float within 5 feet of you, leaving your hands free. Only one weapon can be wielded this way, attempting to float more than one weapon causes both to fall to the ground.",
"Additionally, after you cast a spell that has a casting time of an action, you can make one attack with a weapon as a Bonus Action. When you make a melee weapon attack your reach now increases by 30 feet until the end of your turn."				]
		},
